WEBVTT

00:01.347 --> 00:03.150
In the criminal justice system,

00:03.150 --> 00:06.819
sexually-based offenses
are considered especially heinous

00:06.819 --> 00:08.077
In New York City,

00:08.077 --> 00:11.744
the dedicated detectives who investigate
these vicious felonies are members

00:11.744 --> 00:14.646
of an elite squad known
as The Special Victims Unit.

00:14.646 --> 00:16.670
These are their stories.

00:20.062 --> 00:22.918
Subject 22512-M.

00:22.918 --> 00:24.895
Hemolysis at the time of death.

00:24.895 --> 00:27.316
Lawrence, you make a case
for pink teeth,

00:27.316 --> 00:28.666
you're asking for trouble.

00:28.666 --> 00:31.508
As my students say,
"Bring it on."

00:31.508 --> 00:34.105
Subject 22512-F.

00:34.105 --> 00:36.663
Tissue breakdown
consistent with exposure.

00:36.663 --> 00:38.477
Scavengers aren't eating, though.

00:38.477 --> 00:41.613
What do you expect?
The place is a smorgasbord.

00:44.987 --> 00:46.966
Who put them on the trail?

00:51.514 --> 00:55.750
- These don't belong to us.
- Call the police.

01:02.407 --> 01:04.256
You're contaminating our experiments.

01:04.256 --> 01:06.115
Hey, be careful.
Sorry.

01:06.115 --> 01:08.575
- Are you the SAC?
- You from Special Victims?

01:08.575 --> 01:09.962
Detective Stabler.

01:09.962 --> 01:11.643
Special Agent in Charge,
Rod Franklin.

01:11.643 --> 01:14.868
This is Doctor Talbot.
He runs this facility.

01:15.201 --> 01:17.505
It's a hell of a place
you got here, Doc.

01:17.505 --> 01:19.128
Decay research, Detective.

01:19.128 --> 01:21.529
We study death to help
law enforcement.

01:21.529 --> 01:25.023
Rates of decomp,
cadaver-insect symbiosis,

01:25.023 --> 01:28.006
geology, cadaverine
and putrescine compounds...

01:28.006 --> 01:31.874
Doc, we'll get out of your hair a lot faster
if you'd wait in your office.

01:31.874 --> 01:32.973
Thank you.

01:36.067 --> 01:37.500
How'd they get in here?

01:37.500 --> 01:40.767
We got drag marks inside
and out of the compound.

01:40.767 --> 01:42.544
The unsub parked
on the back country road.

01:42.544 --> 01:43.750
Anyone work here at night?

01:43.750 --> 01:47.097
Strictly a day job, except
for occasional experiments in the lab.

01:47.097 --> 01:49.483
There security cameras?

01:49.483 --> 01:52.454
Only people trying to break in here
are drunken frat boys

01:52.454 --> 01:55.370
and brave Halloween pranksters.

01:55.597 --> 01:56.893
Have you been briefed on the victims?

01:56.893 --> 01:59.220
The two adult IDs were intact.

01:59.220 --> 02:02.327
The Hispanic female
was one of our unit's rape victims.

02:02.327 --> 02:04.601
Detective Benson was the primary.

02:04.601 --> 02:06.586
The minor we're still checking on.

02:06.586 --> 02:09.392
The white male was the father
of a rape-murder victim.

02:09.392 --> 02:11.050
Also my partner's case.

02:11.050 --> 02:14.368
Since you're senior in your department,
you'll act as liaison.

02:14.368 --> 02:17.222
I'll also need you to coordinate your
primary detectives of record

